	dprr:hasNoteText "p. 740" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/3030> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #3030" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "His authority was prolonged so that he might complete his aqueducts (Frontin. Aq. 1.7; see 144, Praetors; and above, on Lepidus Porcina).{473}" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/3015> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #3015" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Received an appropriation of about 180 million HS to repair the Appian, Old Aniensian, and Tepulan aqueducts, and build a new one, the Marcian (Plin. NH 31.41; 36.121; Frontin. Aq. 1.7; cf. Liv. Oxy. Per. 54; Plut. Coriol. 1.1; Grueber, CRRBM 1.485f.; Cesano, Stud. Num. 1 [1942] 209f.)." .
